Interface IHasModelObject

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    ICanController, ICanFilterMask

    @PublishedApi(value=CHANGES_FORBIDDEN)
public interface IHasModelObject
    IHasModelObject provides access to the underlying IModelObject of this wrapper instance.
